INSERT INTO `wp_posts` VALUES (2,1,'2012-03-04 02:32:17','2012-03-04 02:32:17','Great design is all around us, but no matter how many times we admire or take pleasure in a well-designed product, we rarely stop to consider the history and motivation behind it. Recognising this fact, at the end of 2011 Australia-born Asher Compton set about creating a website that would offer insight into the loves, lives and labours of some of the worldâ€™s most talented designers â€“ and so Industry and Interest was born. Each month, Asher, who now lives in Canada, chats to Industry Leaders about their inspirations and aspirations,\r\nusing his signature laid-back interview style to reveal what really makes them tick.','About','','publish','open','open','','about','','','2012-04-06 15:43:15','2012-04-06 22:43:15','',0,'http://spiraldesign.ca/?page_id=2',0,'page','',0),(234,2,'2012-04-01 17:00:49','2012-04-02 00:00:49','','About','','inherit','open','open','','2-revision-27','','','2012-04-01 17:00:49','2012-04-02 00:00:49','',2,'http://iandi.spiraldesign.ca/2-revision-27/',0,'revision','',0),(89,1,'2012-03-04 16:46:03','2012-03-04 16:46:03','Asher Compton is a passionate designer originally from Sydney Australia, now residing in Canada. Industry and interest was launched by Asher at the end of 2011 with the goal to keep people informed as to whatâ€™s happening in the industry and whoâ€™s leading it.\r\n\r\nI&amp;I features regular interviews and posts on Design, Fashion, Super Cars, Photography, Architecture and more.','About','','inherit','open','open','','2-revision-6','','','2012-03-04 16:46:03','2012-03-04 16:46:03','',2,'http://spiraldesign.ca/2-revision-6/',0,'revision','',0),(90,1,'2012-03-04 16:56:48','2012-03-04 16:56:48','','About Custom Fields','','inherit','open','open','','acf_about-custom-fields-3','','','2012-03-04 16:56:48','2012-03-04 16:56:48','',80,'http://spiraldesign.ca/acf_about-custom-fields-3/',0,'revision','',0),(4,1,'2012-03-04 03:02:55','2012-03-04 03:02:5